459
00:37:34.034 --> 00:37:35.777
- Sett deg.
- Takk.


460
00:37:42.585 --> 00:37:45.501
Ekskona. Hun elsket katter.

461
00:37:49.299 --> 00:37:51.969
Hva om vi...

462
00:37:53.888 --> 00:37:57.553
Hva skal vi gjøre?
